29class ExpandedPair

31 DataCharacter _leftChar;
32 DataCharacter _rightChar;
33 FinderPattern _finderPattern;
34 bool _mayBeLast = false;

36public:
37 ExpandedPair() = default;
38 ExpandedPair(const DataCharacter& leftChar, const DataCharacter& rightChar, const FinderPattern& finderPattern, bool mayBeLast) :
39 _leftChar(leftChar), _rightChar(rightChar), _finderPattern(finderPattern), _mayBeLast(mayBeLast) {}
40
41 bool mayBeLast() const {
42 return _mayBeLast;
43 }
44
45 const DataCharacter& leftChar() const {
46 return _leftChar;
47 }
48
49 const DataCharacter& rightChar() const {
50 return _rightChar;
51 }
52
53 const FinderPattern& finderPattern() const {
54 return _finderPattern;
55 }
56
57 bool mustBeLast() const {
58 return !_rightChar.isValid();
59 }
60
61 bool operator==(const ExpandedPair& other) const {
62 return _leftChar == other._leftChar
63 && _rightChar == other._rightChar
64 && _finderPattern.value() == other._finderPattern.value();
65 }
66
67 bool operator!=(const ExpandedPair& other) const {
68 return !(*this == other);
69 }
